Lyrics-Fetcher-LyricsDownload README
====================================

Lyrics::Fetcher::LyricsDownload fetches lyrics from lyricsdownload.com.

It is intended to be used as a fetcher by Lyrics::Fetcher, but
can be used on its own if you desire.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Encode
   HTML::Entities
   HTML::TokeParser
   LWP::Simple
  
Calling Lyrics::Fetcher::LyricsDownload via Lyrics::Fetcher->fetch() is
recommended, but you can call Lyrics::Fetcher::LyricsDownload->fetch() directly
if you want to do so.

